# Required for installing @upstart13-com/* packages from GitHub Packages.
#
# 1. Create a GitHub Classic PAT at https://github.com/settings/tokens/new
#    Scopes: read:packages
#    SSO-authorize for the Upstart13-com org.
# 2. Copy this file to .npmrc and either inline the token or export it:
#       export GITHUB_PAT=ghp_xxx
#       npm install
# 3. .npmrc is gitignored — never commit your token.

@upstart13-com:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com
//npm.pkg.github.com/:_authToken=${GITHUB_PAT}
